00:38:55,776 --> 00:38:57,869
[Screams]

386
00:38:57,978 --> 00:39:00,572
-[Gunshot] -[Blood Splattering]

387
00:39:02,481 --> 00:39:04,881
[Chuckling]

388
00:39:10,489 --> 00:39:12,684
See ya!

389
00:39:14,960 --> 00:39:16,291
[Laughing]

390
00:40:10,510 --> 00:40:12,740
What happened to Hansen?

391
00:40:12,846 --> 00:40:16,247
Oh, he didn't make it, and neither did you.

392
00:40:32,363 --> 00:40:35,855
That's what I always liked about Rudy.

393
00:40:35,967 --> 00:40:38,765
