400
00:41:40,659 --> 00:41:44,254
I don't know. I met him at the office.

401
00:41:44,329 --> 00:41:49,164
Doc, what if we headed south and just kept on goin'?

402
00:41:49,233 --> 00:41:53,829
We got lots of money here. Why share it?

403
00:41:55,072 --> 00:41:58,940
Benyon's kept his end of the bargain so far.

404
00:41:58,975 --> 00:42:02,433
You don't owe Benyon anything.

405
00:42:43,983 --> 00:42:47,475
Try to wrap this up quick. If anything happens, you, uh,

406
00:42:47,520 --> 00:42:49,988
do what you gotta do.

407
00:42:59,330 --> 00:43:01,423
[Sighs]

408
00:43:55,181 --> 00:43:57,945
[Sighing]

409
00:43:57,984 --> 00:44:01,784
