427
00:45:04,578 --> 00:45:07,274
serving a long sentence in a Mexican hellhole;

428
00:45:07,346 --> 00:45:09,576
three, a businessman...

429
00:45:09,682 --> 00:45:11,946
lots of power and influence,

430
00:45:11,984 --> 00:45:14,976
