-[Pouring Drink] -Money.

434
00:45:25,597 --> 00:45:27,792
Maybe there's other considerations.

435
00:45:27,866 --> 00:45:29,800
[Ice Clinking Against Glass]

436
00:45:29,867 --> 00:45:32,301
The wife is very attractive,

437
00:45:32,403 --> 00:45:35,895
and she proves to be willing, very willing.

438
00:45:36,006 --> 00:45:39,999
She sees an opportunity, and she takes it.

439
00:45:40,076 --> 00:45:43,512
And who could blame her? She's tired of life on the run.

440
00:45:43,613 --> 00:45:46,605
Her husband, he's a loser.

441
00:45:46,683 --> 00:45:49,015
She wants something better,

442
00:45:49,085 --> 00:45:51,679
