443
00:45:51,720 --> 00:45:55,520
A very... intimate alliance.

444
00:45:55,624 --> 00:45:59,116
A very pleasurable alliance,

445
00:45:59,194 --> 00:46:03,324
enjoyed by both parties vigorously and repeatedly.

446
00:46:03,397 --> 00:46:06,025
Enjoyed.

447
00:46:06,133 --> 00:46:08,431
And then the moment arrives.

448
00:46:08,502 --> 00:46:11,938
The husband is baited to a remote place,

449
00:46:12,039 --> 00:46:14,735
a place...

450
00:46:14,808 --> 00:46:18,801
Well, Doc, kinda like this.

451
00:46:18,845 --> 00:46:22,542
Don't think too badly of your wife, Doc.

452
00:46:22,649 --> 00:46:25,812
After all, you were locked up in prison,

453
00:46:25,851 --> 00:46:28,752
