00:48:31,666 --> 00:48:33,861
[Grunts]

473
00:48:33,901 --> 00:48:37,166
[Grunting]

474
00:48:37,204 --> 00:48:39,672
Bitch.

475
00:49:12,035 --> 00:49:14,299
-Get in. -Go to hell.

476
00:49:14,338 --> 00:49:16,636
Hey.

477
00:49:17,741 --> 00:49:19,732
Get in.

478
00:49:25,815 --> 00:49:29,444
I guess you did what you had to do to get me out.

479
00:49:33,155 --> 00:49:36,522
You'd do the same for me, wouldn't you, Doc?

480
00:49:36,558 --> 00:49:40,654
You'd humiliate yourself for me, wouldn't you?

481
00:49:42,164 --> 00:49:44,257
Wouldn't you?

