You should just, um, keep...

502
00:51:56,251 --> 00:51:59,516
changing those bandages several times a day.

503
00:51:59,621 --> 00:52:03,113
-[Dog Barking, Whining] -[Cat Meowing]

504
00:52:07,828 --> 00:52:10,888
Looks like I'm gonna need myself a nurse.

505
00:52:16,237 --> 00:52:19,934
Get over there where I can see you. Go on.

506
00:52:23,443 --> 00:52:26,046
[Exhales] That's better.

507
00:52:26,046 --> 00:52:28,344
You know, on second thought,

508
00:52:28,647 --> 00:52:32,344
it might be wiser if we just leave those bandages in place,

509
00:52:32,451 --> 00:52:35,818
'cause I'm nervous about you just irritating that wound.

510
00:52:35,854 --> 00:52:38,550
Is that what you thought, Harold?

511
00:52:38,624 --> 00:52:41,650
-Come here and sit down. -[Cocking Hammer]

512
00:52:41,726 --> 00:52:45,423
