515
00:52:51,168 --> 00:52:53,762
Am I gonna need more lookin' after... or not?

516
00:52:53,870 --> 00:52:56,566
[Stammering] Well, there's...

517
00:52:56,640 --> 00:52:58,767
[Gasps] Yes, there's,

518
