519
00:53:02,378 --> 00:53:04,369
-Oh, lovely. -[Grunts]

520
00:53:07,083 --> 00:53:09,574
-All right. -[Releasing Gun Hammer]

521
00:53:11,053 --> 00:53:14,489
The three of us are gonna do some traveling.

522
00:53:14,556 --> 00:53:17,753
Tomorrow morning, we're gonna take your car and go to El Paso.

523
00:53:17,792 --> 00:53:20,955
No, that... that's just not possible. We...

524
00:53:20,995 --> 00:53:23,463
Look, we can't leave here. Okay?

525
00:53:23,498 --> 00:53:26,956
We've got our work. We've gotta take care of these animals.

526
00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:29,867
What do you say, Fran? Wanna do some travelin'?

527
00:53:29,903 --> 00:53:32,269
Oh,

528
00:53:32,306 --> 00:53:35,366
sure, I mean, whatever you say.

529
00:53:35,408 --> 00:53:38,571
-[Cocking Hammer] -What kind of car you got, Harold?

530
00:53:38,611 --> 00:53:42,809
A Chevy. We have a Chevy Suburban.

531
00:53:42,882 --> 00:53:46,374
Oh, that's nice. I like Chevies.

532
00:53:46,418 --> 00:53:49,819
Why don't you go outside and gas it up?

533
00:53:49,921 --> 00:53:52,617
Check the tires and check the oil.

534
00:53:52,724 --> 00:53:55,124
Make sure it's gonna run real good,

535
00:53:55,227 --> 00:53:57,627
'cause I don't want any trouble on the road.

536
00:53:57,728 --> 00:54:00,629
And if you come back in here with anyone else,

537
00:54:00,731 --> 00:54:03,598
I'm gonna stop her clock.

538
00:54:03,634 --> 00:54:05,829
You got that? She dies.

539
00:54:07,338 --> 00:54:10,603
You do what he says, Harold.

540
00:54:10,640 --> 00:54:13,837
That's right, Harold. Now go on.

541
00:54:13,910 --> 00:54:16,140
Get the fuck outta here.

542
00:54:20,716 --> 00:54:23,150
