543
00:54:23,218 --> 00:54:26,654
Come here, honey. Come here, polka dots. Sit down.

544
00:54:34,662 --> 00:54:36,857
What's his name?

545
00:54:38,332 --> 00:54:40,459
Kitty.

546
00:54:40,568 --> 00:54:43,036
He's cute,

547
00:54:43,069 --> 00:54:45,936
