549
00:54:55,381 --> 00:54:57,872
[Bodyguard #1] Hell, they're probably halfway to Mexico.

550
00:54:57,950 --> 00:55:00,885
[Bodyguard #2] Hansen said they was gonna split the money up in Tucson,

551
00:55:00,953 --> 00:55:04,081
but if they got hot, they'd head to El Paso, the Border Hotel.

552
00:55:04,189 --> 00:55:06,384
Check both places.

553
00:55:06,458 --> 00:55:08,892
Put out the word.

554
00:55:08,960 --> 00:55:11,554
-I know somebody's got our money. -What about Benyon?

555
00:55:11,596 --> 00:55:14,497
[Deer] There's a dry well about a mile from here.

556
00:55:14,598 --> 00:55:17,192
