585
00:58:20,328 --> 00:58:22,694
-Two years. -Hmm.

586
00:58:22,729 --> 00:58:26,130
An exciting two years I'll bet it's been,

587
00:58:26,197 --> 00:58:30,497
hangin' around this place, fixin' up poor little doggies.

588
00:58:30,533 --> 00:58:32,831
Hmm.

589
00:58:36,737 --> 00:58:38,637
Come here.

590
00:58:41,106 --> 00:58:43,404
Look,

591
00:58:43,441 --> 00:58:46,410
I'm not gonna be any trouble to you.

592
00:58:46,443 --> 00:58:51,403
The fact is, this may sound kinda funny, but I was thinkin' that...

