594
00:58:53,747 --> 00:58:58,116
Been my experience that havin' friends is overrated.

595
00:59:00,251 --> 00:59:02,549
Oh, well. [Chuckles]

596
00:59:04,119 --> 00:59:06,212
Come here.

597
00:59:11,857 --> 00:59:15,054
You don't always have to be pointin' that gun at me.

598
00:59:15,160 --> 00:59:18,960
I'll do whatever you want. Really, I will.

599
00:59:19,028 --> 00:59:21,656
What are you wearin' underneath that dress?

600
00:59:21,730 --> 00:59:24,324
Nothin'.

601
00:59:25,265 --> 00:59:27,460
Turn around.

602
00:59:38,306 --> 00:59:40,399
Sit down.

603
00:59:43,709 --> 00:59:48,009
Wipe off that nail polish, 'cause I don't like it. Hey.

604
00:59:48,112 --> 00:59:52,378
When I tell you to come here, you move your ass real fast. You understand?

605
00:59:52,414 --> 00:59:55,383
'Cause I got you figured out from the start.

606
00:59:58,117 --> 01:00:01,678
Now go ahead. Wait a second.

607
01:00:01,720 --> 01:00:04,689
-Get rid of this too. -[Bra Snaps]

608
01:00:06,789 --> 01:00:09,587
Come here.

609
01:00:15,694 --> 01:00:19,186
Don't get blood on me. I hate blood.

610
01:00:30,236 --> 01:00:32,830
I'll park the car while you get the tickets.

611
01:00:32,938 --> 01:00:35,202
-Meet me in the bar. -Okay.

612
01:00:35,239 --> 01:00:37,503
That bag's kind of heavy. Why don't you let me take it?

613
01:00:37,540 --> 01:00:39,804
It's not heavy. I can handle it.

614
01:00:42,443 --> 01:00:44,604
-Hey, you! Don't park here. -[Gasps]

615
01:00:44,645 --> 01:00:48,046
-Use the structure around the corner. -Yes, sir, boss.

616
01:00:58,819 --> 01:01:01,754
Here are your two tickets to El Paso, your change,

617
01:01:01,820 --> 01:01:04,118
