618
01:01:04,155 --> 01:01:07,215
Thank you.

619
01:01:16,262 --> 01:01:18,753
[Woman On P.A.] The train to El Paso has been delayed...

620
01:01:18,864 --> 01:01:20,957
and will be departing in 90 minutes.

621
01:01:21,065 --> 01:01:23,761
The train to El Paso has been delayed...

622
01:01:23,867 --> 01:01:26,165
and will be departing in 90 minutes.

623
