01:13:39,191 --> 01:13:41,792
[Moaning Continues]

733
01:13:41,792 --> 01:13:44,192
[Grunting Continues]

734
01:13:47,096 --> 01:13:49,864
Hey. Hey!

735
01:13:49,864 --> 01:13:53,459
[Fran Giggling] It's Harold!

736
01:13:53,899 --> 01:13:56,959
