737
01:13:57,001 --> 01:14:00,402
Harold, get back in there, you pervert.

738
01:14:00,471 --> 01:14:03,963
-[Fran Laughing] -[Grunting]

739
01:14:04,005 --> 01:14:06,599
[Groaning]

740
01:14:08,007 --> 01:14:10,305
Hey, Gollie, it's Doc.

741
01:14:10,409 --> 01:14:13,310
Yeah. Yeah, right.

742
01:14:13,377 --> 01:14:16,780
How's those travel arrangements coming?

743
01:14:16,780 --> 01:14:20,147
Good. Yeah, she's doing all right.

